{"tid":89712,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[琉球之國] 五日四夜的散心毒撚遊","createTime":"2017-01-21T14:05:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-19T09:50:43.000Z","uid":77106,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7e978e5544d6d00c1dceee16b2b410a9793347e2","tid":89712,"uid":77106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T14:05:29.000Z","msg":"純粹想紀錄返第一次自己去旅行 冇人睇都唔緊要<br />\n今個月頭去左沖繩<br />\n對上一次去日本同朋友一齊去<br />\n跟著佢地遊走大阪十分安心<br />\n<br />\n本身訂機票個陣旅行既目的係純玩樂<br />\n但後尾發生左啲事 心情唔係太好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢次旅行就黎得好合時 就當一個散心既旅行!<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n學我朋友話: 唔開心既事 就擺係日本 唔好帶返黎啦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">Btw識我個啲唔好咁開心以為發現到我ac名<br />\n呢個ac係借返黎<br />\n我邊有咁蠢用自己用開嗰個ac出post</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0632d1ea5e2da94bb9ba12adb662fca84f7b51b9","tid":89712,"uid":77106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T14:09:52.000Z","msg":"Day1 出發!<br />\n<br />\n機要係因航popup&amp;go買既<br />\n點知Book完兩個星期先知香港航空十週年做優惠<br />\n仲平啲 唉唔緊要 都係少少錢<br />\n<br />\n機程大約兩個鐘 一上機坐低我就喊左半個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能係前一晚同朋友傾左少少心事<br />\n起飛前係group到不停msg同我班朋友講對唔住 要佢地擔心我咁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一路打字就一路喊 好彩我隔離個兩個位冇人坐<br />\n<br />\n可能喊得太激動 有個空姐俾左份問卷叫我填 分下心<br />\n空姐: Excuse me, could you please fill in the questionnaire?<br />\n我個陣心諗，我膚色雖然冇咁白姐，唔係以為我係菲律賓籍呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n於是我就話: er&hellip;廣東話得架啦<br />\n點知個空姐都係用返英文同我講野<br />\n我先記起空姐都唔一定識廣東話<br />\n跟著我就拎左份問卷 一拎上手，屌，咁多頁紙既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n柒事唔止呢件<br />\n當我喊完心情平復少少個陣，已經開始派飛機餐<br />\n空姐: 小姐你好，我地今日我地今日A餐係雞肉配薯菜，B餐係牛肉配飯，請問你要邊種?<br />\n因為我仲係迷惘狀態，就諗著叫佢講多次啦<br />\n我: sorry<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n個空姐一聽到我講Sorry，佢以為我聽唔明廣東話，用英文重覆左一次今日有咩食<br />\n咁我冇理由咁柒用廣東話同佢講要B餐架嘛<br />\n所以我就用返英文同佢講: Set B please<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/b43nr0hz\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fb43nr0hz&h=9dd6fb08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本身喊左一輪都冇乜心機食<br />\n但一見到有雪糕! 即刻有食慾<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ml612ctw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fml612ctw&h=fb17c029&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n食完喊完瞓下醒下 眨下眼已經到那霸機場<br />\n都算準時 我記出左海關係日本時間3點3<br />\n<br />\n遲啲再打"},{"pid":"beb9e06c15df063aecbbab2a55e608264900f62e","tid":89712,"uid":77106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T14:24:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Day1 出發!<br />\n<br />\n機要係因航popup&amp;go買既<br />\n點知Book完兩個星期先知香港航空十週年做優惠<br />\n仲平啲 唉唔緊要 都係少少錢<br />\n<br />\n機程大約兩個鐘 一上機坐低我就喊左半個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能係前一晚同朋友傾左少少心事<br />\n起飛前係group到不停msg同我班朋友講對唔住 要佢地擔心我咁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一路打字就一路喊 好彩我隔離個兩個位冇人坐<br />\n<br />\n可能喊得太激動 有個空姐俾左份問卷叫我填 分下心<br />\n空姐: Excuse me, could you please fill in the questionnaire?<br />\n我個陣心諗，我膚色雖然冇咁白姐，唔係以為我係菲律賓籍呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n於是我就話: er&hellip;廣東話得架啦<br />\n點知個空姐都係用返英文同我講野<br />\n我先記起空姐都唔一定識廣東話<br />\n跟著我就拎左份問卷 一拎上手，屌，咁多頁紙既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n柒事唔止呢件<br />\n當我喊完心情平復少少個陣，已經開始派飛機餐<br />\n空姐: 小姐你好，我地今日我地今日A餐係雞肉配薯菜，B餐係牛肉配飯，請問你要邊種?<br />\n因為我仲係迷惘狀態，就諗著叫佢講多次啦<br />\n我: sorry<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n個空姐一聽到我講Sorry，佢以為我聽唔明廣東話，用英文重覆左一次今日有咩食<br />\n咁我冇理由咁柒用廣東話同佢講要B餐架嘛<br />\n所以我就用返英文同佢講: Set B please<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/21/222331_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F21%2F222331_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=bbace49d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本身喊左一輪都冇乜心機食<br />\n但一見到有雪糕! 即刻有食慾<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/21/222341_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F21%2F222341_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=6ae27695&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n食完喊完瞓下醒下 眨下眼已經到那霸機場<br />\n都算準時 我記出左海關係日本時間3點3<br />\n<br />\n遲啲再打</blockquote><br />\n死左圖 睇下點先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a08c0cf730fe4338bd454e9ab08576306d9d6cd","tid":89712,"uid":8815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T03:50:10.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"fa563724b15dc30099275c4ec74785b8d9266941","tid":89712,"uid":77106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T04:00:31.000Z","msg":"真係冇人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過我都會繼續出 當俾自己一個紀念"},{"pid":"9a1968225f571cd7353842b68579fc982722a86b","tid":89712,"uid":52194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T04:03:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cd19644e745eacbaef9c0681f0a8aa66966a842","tid":89712,"uid":75318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T05:05:56.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"cd8bfac3ce8f666c86c8af9d40962166a3ce7957","tid":89712,"uid":42582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T05:41:08.000Z","msg":"去沖繩都有雪糕食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9acea0ab4fd6b3b8920600eb8012ff1564ec0c1","tid":89712,"uid":73311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T05:42:59.000Z","msg":"正皮留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2641430e3059310ced45992e443c46dc54f9ee3b","tid":89712,"uid":19005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T06:06:43.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"4c77f0749565977760454341c87d5c4300d417d6","tid":89712,"uid":78118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T06:10:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"23afd9a11a4c2ecbdb817b18bb0c0e138a831400","tid":89712,"uid":5765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T06:12:05.000Z","msg":"會唔會去潛水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"052b05bb7ea42f545585a0f23c37bebecc82e537","tid":89712,"uid":77106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T06:18:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去沖繩都有雪糕食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有呀<br />\n我見到都好興奮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b983e2374d1f601ad2831c6ff81661d4d9a1c7a2","tid":89712,"uid":77106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T06:18:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>男人老狗喊2個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n男人女人都喊架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇兩個鐘 半個鐘姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c245a30749a3c97ba07a4656e670b27f63e6314","tid":89712,"uid":77106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T06:19:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會唔會去潛水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇去呀<br />\n自己一個 又唔識游水 費事出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41073983b4c862e879a404fbb2e1f11f3d9248b0","tid":89712,"uid":73311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T06:19:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>男人老狗喊2個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/k6wl9vyz\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fk6wl9vyz&h=e1b83606&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7562f582f585fbc05d29df584554d1123e9c832","tid":89712,"uid":78118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T06:19:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7cb6d84378da3009bcea09b7dca2a9a70940b1b8","tid":89712,"uid":77106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T06:26:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>男人老狗喊2個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/k6wl9vyz\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fk6wl9vyz&h=e1b83606&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n當年係舊登見到呢張圖<br />\n笑到傻<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"698563f0b0744dab9d36ba3fb3897395a3997e2e","tid":89712,"uid":77106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T06:27:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>男人老狗喊2個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n男人女人都喊架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇兩個鐘 半個鐘姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n又唔係無朋友,喊咩?!<br />\n我無朋友就話喊者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n心情唔好喊下都係一個抒發情緒既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我怕我忍住會好似以前咁有情緒病<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cad635a75ece20f6ac7eb11a690850a471201eb","tid":89712,"uid":77106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T12:21:18.000Z","msg":"落機就去酒店<br />\n由那霸空港去到酒店 唔使半個鐘<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/xc40gvn1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fxc40gvn1&h=813806cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今次揀左住係國際通附近 係達哥網訂<br />\n<br />\n本身想訂單人房 但點知full左<br />\n咁俾多少少住雙人房 都係差幾十蚊<br />\n呢個酒店好既地方就係樓下有lawson同family mart<br />\n又近國際通<br />\n可惜日用品唔會提供 淨係有杯/毛巾個啲<br />\n好似沖涼/拖鞋就要自備 冇既話大堂都有自助售賣機<br />\nCheck in 安頓好 休息一陣就出發去沖繩縣立博物館美術館<br />\n<br />\n係Omoromachi站落車 行10分鐘就到<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/e7v4hrct\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fe7v4hrct&h=1908d20b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/a64wu2lk\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fa64wu2lk&h=921e0342&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/p6fbgsj4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fp6fbgsj4&h=bdf2f08c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個館分開左博物館同美術館<br />\n因為我之後都會去首里城同海軍壕公園睇歷史個類<br />\n所以今次揀左睇美術館 做下偽文青<br />\n揀左貴少少既門票 可以睇埋今期&ldquo;夢&rdquo;既展覽<br />\n就係上面幅圖 藍色既backdrop<br />\n對我黎講 &ldquo;夢&rdquo;呢個字對我有好大感覺<br />\n可能純粹覺得呢個字好多幻想空間掛<br />\n<br />\n係美術館睇左兩個鐘到 出到黎已經係7點<br />\n就返國際通食野"},{"pid":"5b567a2169cf3a0217098e677e828a03a3a072e2","tid":89712,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T04:37:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d019b2879cae78395d76b07bc69d87112556332","tid":89712,"uid":73371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T09:36:44.000Z","msg":"乖啦<br />\n唔好喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed1e2ba4dc29a3f3b8f34c371c657512d98d80e3","tid":89712,"uid":6520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T10:21:51.000Z","msg":"我睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60aebb45249faa85ad331143a14ac6f9c53f2608","tid":89712,"uid":5765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T10:30:05.000Z","msg":"我四月都去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54356e60f1db6181015922b4c7c04d44ecd15439","tid":89712,"uid":77106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T12:00:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce01bea122e3e5e53838c188db4211f92237843d","tid":89712,"uid":77106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T12:00:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>乖啦<br />\n唔好喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唉唔喊啦<br />\n無謂自己繼續傷春悲秋落去<br />\n覺得自己好不堪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a92dcc5ca061c5b55c2cecdcca84da15640a568","tid":89712,"uid":77106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T12:01:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90389ed3d8dde03abcdb331710eae3b4831a171d","tid":89712,"uid":77106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T12:01:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我四月都去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你去幾多日??<br />\n我有一日join左local tour 都識到個日本妹<br />\n遲啲打出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b687f30d95c688bf75edd11579545281b985507","tid":89712,"uid":34037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T12:23:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bcf345f894e973edf39de75b3b22c94d6af2b38","tid":89712,"uid":5765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T13:40:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我四月都去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你去幾多日??<br />\n我有一日join左local tour 都識到個日本妹<br />\n遲啲打出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n去八日呀我<br />\n我都有諗過join local tour但想窮遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcba1cc91715e9c54d96cbd5b683677da4642b6f","tid":89712,"uid":77106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T16:14:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我四月都去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你去幾多日??<br />\n我有一日join左local tour 都識到個日本妹<br />\n遲啲打出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n去八日呀我<br />\n我都有諗過join local tour但想窮遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我五日四夜咋 全程住係那霸<br />\n所以先join local tour上北部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你8日都住同一個地方定點?"},{"pid":"1b712e5c1e6722f0b64b1e2932c2e8bcae3388e3","tid":89712,"uid":5765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T00:14:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n你去幾多日??<br />\n我有一日join左local tour 都識到個日本妹<br />\n遲啲打出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n去八日呀我<br />\n我都有諗過join local tour但想窮遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我五日四夜咋 全程住係那霸<br />\n所以先join local tour上北部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你8日都住同一個地方定點?</blockquote><br />\n住同一個地方呀，打算自己搭巴士上北部算"},{"pid":"ea3ec5e82446c8fbc11bb5f572bb4a7816184d63","tid":89712,"uid":6520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T04:04:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我四月都去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你去幾多日??<br />\n我有一日join左local tour 都識到個日本妹<br />\n遲啲打出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n去八日呀我<br />\n我都有諗過join local tour但想窮遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n坐路線巴士先係豪遊呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3901de5454d33e8809ad07ee87f704cb5abf32f","tid":89712,"uid":5765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T05:16:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n你去幾多日??<br />\n我有一日join左local tour 都識到個日本妹<br />\n遲啲打出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n去八日呀我<br />\n我都有諗過join local tour但想窮遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n坐路線巴士先係豪遊呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n下，但join local tour幾錢，邊到好"},{"pid":"ebcd6aa399130bbc488cd331afc53af5bf829d20","tid":89712,"uid":77106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T07:31:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n你去幾多日??<br />\n我有一日join左local tour 都識到個日本妹<br />\n遲啲打出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n去八日呀我<br />\n我都有諗過join local tour但想窮遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n坐路線巴士先係豪遊呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n下，但join local tour幾錢，邊到好</blockquote><br />\n我個陣就$380 包埋水族館入場費<br />\n但既然你玩8日 咁一開始住名護<br />\n去到day3/day4再返那霸住都可以呀"},{"pid":"e89fbcfdf252b65175df1d3e7a73ce838f9c2406","tid":89712,"uid":5765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T08:57:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n坐路線巴士先係豪遊呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n下，但join local tour幾錢，邊到好</blockquote><br />\n我個陣就$380 包埋水族館入場費<br />\n但既然你玩8日 咁一開始住名護<br />\n去到day3/day4再返那霸住都可以呀</blockquote><br />\n邊間呀？名護hostel有無好介紹"},{"pid":"eb01fd68aa555754ab99d0ba095a461f1e4bf0af","tid":89712,"uid":77106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T13:03:18.000Z","msg":"睇完美術館 去到縣政府前站 行去國際通<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/b62rqycv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fb62rqycv&h=81f5d482&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nPlan左想食花笠食堂 聽講又平又抵食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁睇下google map點去啦<br />\n點知都要係國際通行去食堂都要15分鐘<br />\n咁唔緊要啦 一路行過去 一路睇下舖頭先<br />\n<br />\n首先食左杯雪糕<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/8unj4s1d\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F8unj4s1d&h=5a3a0f7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係牛奶味既雪糕 但沖繩既雪糕係可以加唔同味既鹽<br />\n個陣我加左綠茶同黃豆粉味<br />\n結論係黃豆粉好食啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有辣椒 胡椒 但冇咩興趣 所以冇落到<br />\n<br />\n跟著就見到好多賣風獅既舖頭<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/eyocr4s8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Feyocr4s8&h=6d76b11b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/9hudjncg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F9hudjncg&h=ee3fa496&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n風獅係吉祥物 寓意可以幫你捉住同守護幸運同幸福<br />\n自己都買左個做紀念 因為幾可愛<br />\n而且好耐之前有睇過林詠琛既小說 有一本係以沖繩作題材<br />\n所以對風獅有好深印象<br />\n<br />\n沿途見到好多卡通人物既公仔<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/lmwbv5he\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Flmwbv5he&h=f288c8a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n又係呢隻亂叫既雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ng86fe4j\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fng86fe4j&h=a35176e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n終於行到花笠食堂<br />\n點知收9點 原來係行下hea下已經9點<br />\n屌 好後悔冇睇清楚時間 好肚餓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以要再搵有咩餐廳唔太貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n食堂附近有條橫街叫平和通<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ek3oj765\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fek3oj765&h=3d38e800&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但冇咩好睇 <br />\n第一牧志公設市場就係裡面<br />\n可惜我一個人唔食到太多 所以冇去到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n終於搵到間啱食既餐廳<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/bt9ux124\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fbt9ux124&h=d1d72fc4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/zkeq4ap3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fzkeq4ap3&h=33aa48dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢有俾一小碟既前菜 炸雞既物體 <br />\n酸酸甜甜好好食<br />\n叫左杯菠蘿汁 沖繩豬軟骨麵 同花生豆腐<br />\n沖繩既豆腐同香港個啲完全唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n勁有咬口 唔係一咬就散 好好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而佢啲麵唔係拉麵 唔識形容 但又係好好食!<br />\n買單好似2300yen到 已經係我個幾日最貴既一餐<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/i2dxlm01\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fi2dxlm01&h=dc89bf94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n食食下中途仲有人表演 好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n食完之後就慢步行路返去酒店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又係一路行 一路入舖頭睇下有咩賣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/6wrlb7zj\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F6wrlb7zj&h=9b12c63f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢個細路本身以為佢趴左係枱<br />\n睇真啲原來係假既 嚇死我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n返到酒店11點到 沖完涼就plan第二日行邊<br />\n搵好巴士路線就瞓教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nDay 1完"},{"pid":"6da9e7bcc6d9a74339f8345d45a904f59f31dece","tid":89712,"uid":77106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T13:07:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n坐路線巴士先係豪遊呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n下，但join local tour幾錢，邊到好</blockquote><br />\n我個陣就$380 包埋水族館入場費<br />\n但既然你玩8日 咁一開始住名護<br />\n去到day3/day4再返那霸住都可以呀</blockquote><br />\n邊間呀？名護hostel有無好介紹</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.klook.com/zh-TW/activity/828-hip-hop-bus-okinawa/?aid=34\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.klook.com%2Fzh-TW%2Factivity%2F828-hip-hop-bus-okinawa%2F%3Faid%3D34&d=INALvyyzIH9cpXQf1t%2F%2BEnvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=53e3a94d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.klook.com/zh-TW/activity/828-hip-hop-bus-okinawa/?aid=34</a><br />\n我參加左呢個local tour 而家仲平啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n至於名護hostle就唔知啦 因為冇住名護<br />\n唔好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4326ad319ba3b6250f58ed6a29766db4643ecaa1","tid":89712,"uid":5765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T13:59:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n我個陣就$380 包埋水族館入場費<br />\n但既然你玩8日 咁一開始住名護<br />\n去到day3/day4再返那霸住都可以呀</blockquote><br />\n邊間呀？名護hostel有無好介紹</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.klook.com/zh-TW/activity/828-hip-hop-bus-okinawa/?aid=34\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.klook.com%2Fzh-TW%2Factivity%2F828-hip-hop-bus-okinawa%2F%3Faid%3D34&d=INALvyyzIH9cpXQf1t%2F%2BEnvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=53e3a94d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.klook.com/zh-TW/activity/828-hip-hop-bus-okinawa/?aid=34</a><br />\n我參加左呢個local tour 而家仲平啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n至於名護hostle就唔知啦 因為冇住名護<br />\n唔好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果我join左佢，我諗我gogo pass都可以慳返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9733394902a34f09facf0b14a7822e43203d7a22","tid":89712,"uid":34427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T02:13:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"501d3f936aca1940c5caf25bfc7b30ff66774300","tid":89712,"uid":6520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T03:14:29.000Z","msg":"花笠食過麻麻地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但選擇係好多既"},{"pid":"af29a423a375a857f608f429d2dc26005ae82344","tid":89712,"uid":2127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T13:47:31.000Z","msg":"個趴喺到嘅細路係假人？<br />\n咁真嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bbd81004aceb84ce7774d44053375801018894d","tid":89712,"uid":2127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T13:47:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>花笠食過麻麻地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但選擇係好多既</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實係食咩架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee6c4f629bb140d49bf005beef50d80f07a1490f","tid":89712,"uid":77106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T13:55:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個趴喺到嘅細路係假人？<br />\n咁真嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係假架 我都嚇左一嚇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70ae298b61ea76db783a792dd6131cb36770838a","tid":89712,"uid":77106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T13:56:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>花笠食過麻麻地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但選擇係好多既</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實係食咩架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n家常便飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?<br />\n唔知可唔可以咁講呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83c597da492b92357ab3a4e87ea0b95bb3039e93","tid":89712,"uid":56206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T09:41:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"163ce33bec5513422280e2a917d79f95c520441e","tid":89712,"uid":80270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T15:41:37.000Z","msg":"快d update la,有人睇架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57b06b8ef30d54eb91973be50cfb86451f942ab6","tid":89712,"uid":66759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T15:48:00.000Z","msg":"不錯"},{"pid":"d7032ca3fc78b60231290362b29d82ce49a284cd","tid":89712,"uid":77106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T11:46:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>快d update la,有人睇架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n原來有人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗著過左假期沉底算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽晚出啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aff8fa53288a70be261a7f797c1ed72665c7fec6","tid":89712,"uid":77106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T16:47:26.000Z","msg":"Day2<br />\n本身朝早想去附近既cafe叫萬丸食早餐<br />\n見台灣既遊記都好推薦呢間<br />\n因為你叫一杯野飲 就送早餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而且呢間又近我住既酒店 咁梗係去食下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.biteamap.com/blog/post/434481431-%E6%B2%96%E7%B9%A9-x-%E7%94%98%E5%91%B3%E8%99%95%E8%90%AC%E4%B8%B8-x-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E9%80%9A%E8%B2%B7%E9%A3%B2%E6%96%99%E9%80%81%E6%97%A9%E9%A4%90!\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.biteamap.com%2Fblog%2Fpost%2F434481431-%25E6%25B2%2596%25E7%25B9%25A9-x-%25E7%2594%2598%25E5%2591%25B3%25E8%2599%2595%25E8%2590%25AC%25E4%25B8%25B8-x-%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E9%2580%259A%25E8%25B2%25B7%25E9%25A3%25B2%25E6%2596%2599%25E9%2580%2581%25E6%2597%25A9%25E9%25A4%2590%21&d=INALvyyzIH9cpXQf1t%2F%2BEnvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=d968930b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.biteamap.com/blog/post/434481431-%E6%B2%96%E7%B9%A9-x-%E7%94%98%E5%91%B3%E8%99%95%E8%90%AC%E4%B8%B8-x-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E9%80%9A%E8%B2%B7%E9%A3%B2%E6%96%99%E9%80%81%E6%97%A9%E9%A4%90!</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">點知星期日唔開!</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<br />\n唉咁就直接搭monorail去首里 諗住lawson買個包就上路啦<br />\n點知係首里站行出去 行左一陣都搵唔到有便利店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而且天氣唔太好 一路行 一路落雨<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/fi7e3htl\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ffi7e3htl&h=b3a04ebf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行左一陣終於搵到間超級市場 狗衝入去買早餐先<br />\n好肚餓呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後買左啲炸物 凍左 麻麻地好食<br />\n但總算醫飽個肚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/vr4fmo3x\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fvr4fmo3x&h=2e5d2d8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n越落越大雨 行到去藝術大學<br />\n就會見到首里城啦<br />\n一路行 一路見好多呢啲鴨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/2bjvwq38\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F2bjvwq38&h=c82f9592&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一堆堆係草度行黎行去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/2wzoqdvk\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F2wzoqdvk&h=bffc6628&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個好似係世界遺產黎 叫園比屋武御嶽石門<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/o413sxbv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fo413sxbv&h=f38d5c32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔得啦真係太大雨 去左避左半個鐘雨 先繼續行<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔通連個天都唔鐘意我?</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/cmfqydzg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fcmfqydzg&h=a94cfb4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行到最上 就要買飛入場<br />\n如果你買左monorail一日通 有折扣<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/nxbfi7h0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fnxbfi7h0&h=29f380b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n裡面啲展品相就唔post啦 太多lu<br />\n大約行左一個半鐘 就去左食飯啦<br />\n<br />\n午餐食琉球茶坊 就係首里城入口附近<br />\n揀左薑汁agu豬既set 好好食!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/liux69pc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fliux69pc&h=7edc5b23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/4ihjsrb2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F4ihjsrb2&h=c58df866&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}